              <p>TapToTravel works offline! All events are stored locally on the device and synced automatically when
                connectivity returns. You can complete your ride even without internet.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">
              <h3>How is the fare calculated?</h3>
              <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
            </div>
