              <p>Fare is calculated in real-time using GPS data from the driver's device. It considers both distance
                traveled and time taken, ensuring fair and transparent pricing.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">
              <h3>What payment methods are supported?</h3>
